<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.6.8">
<l>nilaiyāḷā kaveṉṉai yukantāṉai nilamakaḷtaṉ</l>
<l>mulaiyāḷvit takaṉai mutunāṉmaṟai vītitoṟum</l>
<l>alaiyārkaṭal pōlmuḻaṅkum teṉṉaḻuntaiyil maṉṉiniṉṟa</l>
<l>kalaiyārcoṟ poruḷaik kaṇṭukoṇṭuka ḷittēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having seen for myself the one who desired me</l>
<l rend="indent">to become his permanent servant,</l>
<l>The able one who reigns over the breasts of the lady earth,</l>
<l>The meaning of the words of the treatises who stands eternally</l>
<l rend="indent">in Aḻuntai of the south</l>
<l>Where on every street resound, like the wave-filled sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">the four ancient Vedas, I was reeling!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
